{"tid":369092,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"你地睇小說/戲/劇，鍾意知左個結局先定跟返作者鋪排去睇？","createTime":"2017-08-22T04:48:18.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-26T10:56:18.000Z","uid":21414,"like":10,"dislike":10,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"b932d58db51b5c6d3f09e70ff444b2d9371d7da8","tid":369092,"uid":21414,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-22T04:48:19.000Z","msg":"有d人鍾意睇左結局先<br />\n閱讀習慣反映一個人性格，直接睇結局既人唔鍾意轉彎抹角，<br />\n而睇左個結局再轉頭睇返作者點樣合理地將個故事lead去某個特定結局，<br />\n會令到讀者能夠更深入了解作者寫作既背後動機、細節上既巧妙，<br />\n會更好地同書本有深層次既心靈連結，而非純求心理刺激，睇結局唔代表失去過程中既驚喜<br />\n<br />\n心理學家嘅睇法:<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.google.com.hk/amp/s/amp.theguardian.com/books/booksblog/2011/aug/17/spoilers-enhance-enjoyment-psychologists\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.google.com.hk%2Famp%2Fs%2Famp.theguardian.com%2Fbooks%2Fbooksblog%2F2011%2Faug%2F17%2Fspoilers-enhance-enjoyment-psychologists&d=wlJq7LVdHrOkDtjVdIz6VNr9upuAghWR75VkZoMWgf8%3D&h=6bf3779c\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.google.com.hk/amp/s/amp.theguardian.com/books/booksblog/2011/aug/17/spoilers-enhance-enjoyment-psychologists</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n我自己就鍾意享受返作者個鋪排，尤其點樣埋伏筆，點樣張幾個storyline merge 埋一齊<br />\n<br />\n我亦覺得個作者鋪排得咁辛苦，埋伏筆，我相信每個小說/戲劇作者都想讀者享受佢個鋪排<br />\n<br />\n追劇嘅時候如果有劇透post我一定唔會入，會盡量避免被劇透<br />\n<br />\n睇小說去到緊張位我直情會用手㩒住，一行一行睇，廢事唔小心𥄫到之後嗰幾句<br />\n<br />\n如果睇偵探小說有人係第一頁就寫左邊個係兇手，真係會破壞哂我嘅期待<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n大家支持邊方？<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> : 睇左結局/飛住黎睇<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> : 跟返作者鋪排睇<br />\n<br />\n歡迎大家投票之餘，再講下自己觀點同討論<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9f112b192b068fb0988a790d594ef8d4eebf64d3","tid":369092,"uid":3296,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-22T05:28:09.000Z","msg":"追本小說/漫畫之類追追下有時好期待個結局(如有)<br />\n成日忍唔住去望下結局會係點，比如兩條友最後有冇一齊<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 但搞到如果happy ending/滿意還好，bad end即刻無癮唔想睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"00af82cd82ab2ac4aeeea7365283d5944101bdca","tid":369092,"uid":66240,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-22T06:52:23.000Z","msg":"跳去結局先再睇故既比起順住編排睇既既感覺差好遠<br />\n順住睇先有FEEL"},{"pid":"028821d21fa3be4d6eb768da4326a3a3a32473f0","tid":369092,"uid":56157,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-22T06:54:38.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>跳去結局先再睇故既比起順住編排睇既既感覺差好遠<br />\n順住睇先有FEEL</blockquote><br />\n其實如果作者一開波想做呢個效果(睇結局先再睇故)。一早用倒敘法寫啦"},{"pid":"de746c1049f729d71b2b038c29d8ecbfa6b62e46","tid":369092,"uid":21414,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-22T12:36:20.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>跳去結局先再睇故既比起順住編排睇既既感覺差好遠<br />\n順住睇先有FEEL</blockquote><br />\n其實如果作者一開波想做呢個效果(睇結局先再睇故)。一早用倒敘法寫啦</blockquote><br />\n同埋翻睇都可以做到睇結局先嘅效果"},{"pid":"55e1439022b26aacb66a870e27ee174495747644","tid":369092,"uid":129043,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-22T12:41:20.000Z","msg":"睇結局先同被人劇透一樣<br />\n不過仲要慘一萬倍<br />\n<br />\n跟返作者<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"30f336071eeddfdc3215e34f4da1c1b3fa734253","tid":369092,"uid":11185,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-22T12:49:11.000Z","msg":"視乎咩作品，文藝少少既話劇透左都冇所謂，反正過程比結果重要"},{"pid":"2927632c48d829d6110464a92aa95f6fdf393254","tid":369092,"uid":24596,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-22T13:01:03.000Z","msg":"我鐘意先睇結局<br />\n因為咁會令我更想睇中間嘅內容<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ced7609d586c13597edee878e4a3c9be641d6d1b","tid":369092,"uid":1248,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-22T13:10:01.000Z","msg":"順住睇感受作者想比我既喜怒哀樂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1ca4bada3cd7aaf8bbb39e186c886b40e57664d0","tid":369092,"uid":30347,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-26T10:56:18.000Z","msg":"平時都順住睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n不過，有時候知道咗結局先有興趣睇原本無理過嘅作品"}]}